text: Éder Diego Holanda do Nascimento, known as Éder Diego (born 17 April 1985) is a Brazilian football player who plays for União de Leiria. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Segunda Liga for Desportivo das Aves on 16 August 2009 in a game against Freamunde. ==References== ==External links== Category:1985 births Category:Sportspeople from Belém Category:Living people Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal Category:S.C.
